---
title: Mild Indian Double White Fish Curry with Roasted Veggies & Basmati Rice
description: Delicately spiced and luxuriously creamy, this mild curry is sure to hit the spot! It’s packed full of flaky white fish and roasted veggies, making it ultra satiating - serve it over fluffy basmati rice and dig in!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67c0f5e460686822766eb407-d5323bb1.jpeg
